parameters: \}Do you know the girl from the second year class who likes to speak to the vending machine?\{
你知道二年级那个喜欢对着自动贩卖机说话的女生吗？
\}No I'm not thinking about being an idol !!!!\{
我才没有想当偶像的意思呢！！！
\}Did you just hear neko's sound up there?\{
上面好像有猫咪的声音？
\}But the rooftop will only open at noon...\{
\}Do you know about this activity room?\{
你知道这个活动部室吗？
\}It has been closed ever since I came to this school, but no one knows why...\{
我入学之前就已经一直大门紧闭了，没有人知道为什么……
\}And I also heard that you could see some lights coming out from the room every night...\{
而且我听说那里每天晚上都会从门缝里透出亮光……
\#门锁上了，而且在门口上还贴着“请加入我们一起拯救废校”
\#这扇门从不知道什么时候开始就被封上了
